&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;
Workshop III:&lt;br /&gt;Joint Technology Initiative - Innovative Medicines Initiative 2
&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;
Workshop IV:&lt;br /&gt;Joint Technology Initiative - Bio-Based Industries Joint Undertaking
